Codecademy offers a helpful, free, online course that covers the basics of HTML & CSS syntax:

http://www.codecademy.com/tracks/web (Links to an external site.)

Work your way through as much of the course as you can. If you get stuck in any given lesson, move on to the next lesson, and keep yourself moving!

Make a submission when you've completed each one of the 3 separate parts. Submit a link to your code academy account (https://www.codecademy.com/[username])

Create a comment on your submission with 1) the amount of time this took you and how you spent it , and 2) your observations and 3) questions from this assignment.